Text:
Hello, thanks for the great book. I am new here and have been trying to find two books, didn't know if you could help or not. They are:
Impossible Odds: The Kidnapping of Jessica Buchanan and Her Dramatic Rescue by Seal Team 6.
Battle Ready: Memoir of a Seal Warrior Medic.
If you could find these, or if any one else knows where to find them I would be in your debt.
